Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.41,0:00:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot approve of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could have defeated them both, \Nyet you allowed them to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Killing them right away wouldn't be any fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should chase the rabbit until it can no longer \Nrun, and kill it at the height of its terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But considering that you revealed \NBerserker's Noble Phantasm,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you should have \Nkilled at least one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way to counter \NBerserker's Noble Phantasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noble Phantasm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once every three days, restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you don't feel pity for Emiya Shirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know I lack that emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will make him suffer in Kiritsugu's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your injuries seem to have healed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:54.58,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(303,490)}#04   Finding the Will to Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tohsaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pick one thing to be surprised about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I passed out, and you carried me back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't as dumb as you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's very interesting. Well, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should have said it earlier, but thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you thanking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you saved me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't thank an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Grail War is a fight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just didn't feel like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking someone in their sleep isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it was a blunder on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lowered my guard, maybe because I'm more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could say I have some emotional flab.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emotional flab?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that you're fat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a funny boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time we meet, it will be as enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are we finally going home, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go home empty-handed, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make amends for my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Saber?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber, what are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have been resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should, at least, \Nget into peak condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, how are your injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, I am impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did not expect you to possess self-healing magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, regarding last night, there is \Nsomething I feel I must say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must ask that you, my Master, \Nrefrain from such actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What choice did I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You would place so much confidence \Nin a Servant you've only just met?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We shook on it, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your words are gratifying to me, as a Servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the future, please restrain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would have you win the Grail for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want the Holy Grail, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that I might fulfill my own wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We Servants are Heroic Spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a result of that fame, when we \Nmake known our true identities,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we also reveal our weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you have me call you "Saber" \Nto hide your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Grail summons seven Servants,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,each selected based on their class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Class? Like swordsman or bowman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Grail prepares seven vessels in advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and summons Heroic Spirits from \Nall eras that match those vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are the seven classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber, Lancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer, Rider, Caster,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assassin, and Berserker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a hero, you were proficient with a sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you were summoned in the Saber class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Conversely, however, that is also \Nthe Saber class's shortcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shortcoming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example, faced with an opponent more \Nskilled in close-quarters combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I couldn't win in a head-on attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't attack directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, we possess what are \Ncalled "Noble Phantasms."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancer's spear, Archer's bow, and my sword \Nare all examples of Noble Phantasms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noble Phantasms are Servants' secret weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, a significant amount of mana \Nis required for their activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you can't use them carelessly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, a Servant must call out the Noble \NPhantasm's true name when activating it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so they run the risk of revealing their identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then that's why you make your sword invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, I have a favor to ask, related to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It concerns my true name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, a Servant reveals their identity to their \NMaster, so they can formulate a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, you are unskilled as a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is a chance that an experienced \Nmage could read your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you can't reveal your name to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave your Noble Phantasm's \Nuse to your discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's decided, let's have breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before I forget, where did \Nthose clothes come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rin gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said that, since I cannot dematerialize, \NI require ordinary clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she wears prim and proper outfits like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:06.65,News,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DO NOT ENTER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's faint, but I sense mana residue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that was no simple gas leak accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could they involve ordinary people in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Master is supposed to replenish you, \Nbut since I'm such a novice, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can minimize my mana expenditure by sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.19,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Homurahara Academy \NArchery Dojo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Emiya residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:47.28,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Fujimura here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuji-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? I'm a little busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.12,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving up my day off for my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, make me a lunch and bring \Nit to the archery dojo ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.36,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That will be all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't Masters supposed to \Navoid attracting attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something like last night won't happen now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there is always a possibility, however small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allowing you to walk alone wouldn't be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber, if someone tries to talk to you, \Njust shake your head without replying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be best if you'd act like you \Ndon't know Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense residual mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something feels off, but it doesn't \Nseem to pose any danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said it was safe, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here with a lunch for Fuji-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind calling her for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, am I glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have her lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimura-sensei's been a handful. \NWhen she's hungry, she gets high-strung.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you check first thing in the \Nmorning to see if she had her lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was really tired, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji again? Where is he today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Playing hooky. I think he has a new girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, Emiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that woman out front?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was gorgeous. Is she a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's kind of complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Was"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuki-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's an acquaintance of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's sort of here to check out the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've never had a student from another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she enrolled, she'd be an object of curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she's a friend, look out for her, Emiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, Emiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Outdoor shoes are forbidden in the school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Visitors' Lounge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, about that instructor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sense something about Kuzuki-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, at first, he struck me as \Nbeing more than he seemed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he is not a mage, nor does he smell of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Kuzuki-sensei turned out to be \Na mage, I'd be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you mean, "more than he seemed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His breathing was exceedingly \Nnatural and composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, I was quite impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even his gait was perfectly efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His pupils must be at ease with \Nsuch a man as their teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we proceed to the next location?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you want to go all around the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, until I have ascertained that it is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Emiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're still at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're already done?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're wrapping up early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, keep up the hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Emiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you ever come back to the archery club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Fujimura-sensei \Nis trying to talk you into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but where do you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once I get things sorted out, I'm thinking \Nof giving it another shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the minute you joined, \Nyou were so good, it was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it always seemed like you weren't \Ninterested in hitting the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you didn't have the desire to hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just assumed you quit because you got bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you have no desire for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying you should be like Shinji, \Nbut why not try to have some fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, if I'm getting pity from a classmate, \Nit must be really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you never crack a smile, Emiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we were all being rowdy, you were the \None who didn't laugh at my best material.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still holding a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I need to go to the faculty room, \Nso I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuzuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's been following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know her, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my old man knew her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiritsugu-san knew her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She came to visit Kiritsugu-san, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be staying at my place \Nfor a while, so be nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Staying at my place"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're shacking up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't shacking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber will only be staying \Nhere for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Saber-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'd really appreciate it if you'd \Ntry to be friends with her, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I can do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimura-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you giving her your approval \Nto stay, Fujimura-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a teacher, I'd have to say absolutely not,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't turn away a girl who's come \Nhere to see Kiritsugu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as a homestay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:56.10,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Temperatures are expected to fall again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I pulled out all the stops for this dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:59.00,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please exercise caution when driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Sakura isn't coming to help, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:05.74,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Up next, we have the weather report.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuji-nee, it's getting late. \NMind walking Sakura home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:06.70,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.23,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Now, for tomorrow's forecast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuji-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:12.33,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The Japanese islands are under a strong, \Nwintry pressure-distribution pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:16.21,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It looks like this may bring nasty weather, \Nwith a focus on northern Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me, Fujimura-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:19.96,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Take a look at how the clouds \Nhave moved since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, request denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to walk Sakura-chan home for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:23.76,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The small clouds that had \Nformed over the Sea of Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.84,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and northern Japan are moving \Nto the east, toward the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because starting today, I'll be staying here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Care to join me, Sakura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can call your folks, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can always count on you, Fujimura-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's use the tatami mat room in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of futons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind, do you, Saber-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of incense is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A witch's potion, most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Possibly a poison that supposedly destroys love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, we're dealing with a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever her resentment, it must be powerful \Nto have made her into a Servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enough talk. I'm opening a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The flow is toward Ryuudou Temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the stolen life force is all flowing \Ntoward the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit behind the coma \Nincidents is probably Caster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A witch inhabiting Ryuudou Temple, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That means we made a mistake last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Berserker to a draw, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that was the optimal outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Caster's spread such a wide net, \Nshe must have observed last night's battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, we tipped our hand, \Nwhile failing to defeat our opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:20:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll track Caster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can still sense her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put an end to this before she \Ncan flee to Ryuudou Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your policy is to avoid things \Nyou know are beyond you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think this is a special case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be satisfied until you start a fight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're ignoring an easily-defeated opponent, \Nand going after the most difficult one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can take him out whenever we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just choosing to ignore him, as long \Nas he stays hidden at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what if Emiya Shirou comes to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,still choosing to ignore that he is a Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I owe nothing to someone who \Ndoesn't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura and I understand one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I know the most about my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I cannot give you the Command Seals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall kill you gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.82,0:23:40.05,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(512,1)}Next time \NDancing After School
